An moronis.

Ἰ And yf ye can not fynde a laten werde, or englysshe worde acordynge to your purpose, in thys present boke so shall ye take ortus vocabulorum, the vhyche is more redyer to fynden a latyn words after the ABC. and englysshe therof folowynge for thys boke is thus ordened for to fynde a laten after ony maner of worde in englysshe for them that wyl Ieme to wryte or spelte latyn. and because that uo man or chylde shall heraster haue ony diffyculte more to serche for ony latyn or englysshe worde. ther-

fore ve haue ordened this lybell in smal volum for to bynde with Ortus vocabulorum moost necessary for chyldren.

Ἰ Ad laudem et honorem omnipotentis dei et intemerate genitricis eius finit excellentissimum opus scolasticis anglie qnam maxime necessarium. qnod merito medulla grammatices apud nos, vel paruulorum promptua- rium nuncupatur. Impressum Londouiis per wynandum de worde in vico anglice (the flete strete) appellato sub solis intersignio commorantem. Anno domini. mmcccc- xvi. die vero v. mensis Septembris.
